.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, house, d&b, dubstep, folk
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, paramedic, social-worker, writer
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the fan of house is on the right of the writer##1
5. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
6. the paramedic is on the far right##1
7. the writer is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | indie        | d&b | house | folk |
| Job     | fisherman | social-worker | writer  | nurse   | paramedic |

