.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, orchid, azalea, marigold
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person who growszinnia is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Flower   | bellflower | azalea | orchid | marigold | zinnia     |

