.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
There 5 different types of food: cucumber, avocado, nectarine, spinach, cherry
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Food       | spinach   | nectarine   | avocado | cherry | cucumber |
| Transport   | helicopter | quad-bike | roller   | skateboard | car       |

