.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony, rabbit, rat
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, baking, traveling, board-games, hiking
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | frog   | pony  | rat      | chinchilla | rabbit     |
| Hobby   | board-games | traveling | baking | fishing   | hiking |

