2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Birthday   | march | june | september | february | may |
| Pet           | rat      | fish    | goldfish  | dog     | frog     |

