.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There 5 different types of food: apple, artichoke, avocado, cherry, pomegranate
There are 5 different nationalities: german, brazilian, pakistani, nigerian, mexican
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the brazilian is the person eating cherry##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the nigerian##1
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the german##1
7. the mexican is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | cherry | apple  | avocado | artichoke | pomegranate |
| Nationality    | brazilian    | nigerian | mexican   | german       | pakistani        |

