.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, mystery, crime, romance
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse, surfing, weightlifting
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero | crime          | mystery    | romance | scientific  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | biathlon | surfing | cricket |

