4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Hobby      | reading | drawing | magic-tricks      | sudoku | collecting      |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican       | argentine | turkish  | indonesian |

