.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
House: cape-cod, futuristic, art-deco, colonial, tower
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, french, indian, nigerian, thai
1. the nigerian is on the right of the indian##1
2. the colonial house is on the left of the thai##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the indian is the art-deco house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
6. the french is on the left of the art-deco house##1
7. the thai is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| House           | colonial     | tower | cape-cod | art-deco  | futuristic |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai               | french     | indian | nigerian |

