.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, gospel, hip-hop, house, rock
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, february, april, january, july
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of blues##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of blues is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
6. the fan of house is the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | hip-hop    | rock | house   | gospel |
| Birthday     | february | may | january | april | july    |

