6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Flower   | zinnia     | orchid       | marigold     | iris  | tulip  |
