.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, bus, motorbike, train, van
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, goat, hamster, mouse
1. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Transport   | bus | van | motorbike | subway | train |
| Pet           | mouse | hamster  | frog    | chinchilla  | goat   |

 